description: Laxton`s Dugtrio was captured by Goh. It was the leader of a group of Diglett on Laxton`s farm and they were displaced into his field after Team Rocket affected their habitat and forced them to move. Dugtrio battled Team Rocket while it was Goh`s Pok√©mon and defeated them. Goh left Dugtrio with Laxton as he realized the Diglett would be in big trouble without their leader.
name: Dugtrio (Endou)
